        "discover": {
            "title": "Discover Our Olive Oil",
            "content": "<p class='text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6'>Our extra virgin olive oil comes from carefully selected olives harvested during the <strong>second season</strong> — the precise moment when green, red, and black varieties reach their perfect balance of maturity. This meticulous timing ensures an oil that is harmonious, stable, and generously aromatic.</p><h2>A Unique Blend</h2><details class='group mb-6 text-gray-600'><summary class='cursor-pointer list-none outline-none leading-relaxed [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden'><span class='group-open:hidden'>ZABRA blends <strong>Arbequina</strong> and <strong>Local</strong> olive varieties to achieve a stable golden color and a smooth, subtly fruity flavor profile... <span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] ml-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline'>Read more</span></span><span class='hidden group-open:block'><p class='leading-relaxed mb-3'>ZABRA blends <strong>Arbequina</strong> and <strong>Local</strong> olive varieties to achieve a stable golden color and a smooth, subtly fruity flavor profile with a peppery finish. Each batch is pressed within hours of harvest to preserve the full freshness of the aromas.</p><span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline cursor-pointer'>Show less</span></span></summary></details><h2>Tasting Tips</h2><details class='group mb-6 text-gray-600'><summary class='cursor-pointer list-none outline-none leading-relaxed [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden'><span class='group-open:hidden'>To reveal its full richness, drizzle it over warm bread, a fresh salad, or a tagine... <span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] ml-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline'>Read more</span></span><span class='hidden group-open:block'><p class='leading-relaxed mb-3'>To reveal its full richness, drizzle it over warm bread, a fresh salad, or a tagine at the end of cooking. It elevates every dish without overpowering the flavors.</p><span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline cursor-pointer'>Show less</span></span></summary></details>"
        },
        "why-zabira": {
            "title": "Why Choose ZABRA?",
            "content": "<p>At ZABRA, every bottle tells the story of an <strong>artisanal craft</strong> passed down through generations. We don't mass-produce — we select.</p><h2 class='flex items-center mt-10 mb-4'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' class='inline-block mr-3 text-[rgba(212,175,55,0.9)]'><path d='M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z'></path><path d='M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12'></path></svg>Second Season Harvest</h2><details class='group mb-6 text-gray-600'><summary class='cursor-pointer list-none outline-none leading-relaxed [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden'><span class='group-open:hidden'>Unlike early industrial harvests, we wait for the <strong>second season</strong> of maturation... <span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] ml-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline'>Read more</span></span><span class='hidden group-open:block'><p class='leading-relaxed mb-3'>Unlike early industrial harvests, we wait for the <strong>second season</strong> of maturation. This longer process allows the olives to develop superior aromatic complexity, with notes of ripe fruit, fresh grass, and sweet almond.</p><span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline cursor-pointer'>Show less</span></span></summary></details><h2 class='flex items-center mt-10 mb-4'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' class='inline-block mr-3 text-[rgba(212,175,55,0.9)]'><path d='M12.22 2h-.44a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v.18a2 2 0 0 1-1 1.73l-.43.25a2 2 0 0 1-2 0l-.15-.08a2 2 0 0 0-2.73.73l-.22.38a2 2 0 0 0 .73 2.73l.15.1a2 2 0 0 1 1 1.72v.51a2 2 0 0 1-1 1.74l-.15.09a2 2 0 0 0-.73 2.73l.22.38a2 2 0 0 0 2.73.73l.15-.08a2 2 0 0 1 2 0l.43.25a2 2 0 0 1 1 1.73V20a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h.44a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-.18a2 2 0 0 1 1-1.73l.43-.25a2 2 0 0 1 2 0l.15.08a2 2 0 0 0 2.73-.73l.22-.39a2 2 0 0 0-.73-2.73l-.15-.08a2 2 0 0 1-1-1.74v-.5a2 2 0 0 1 1-1.74l.15-.09a2 2 0 0 0 .73-2.73l-.22-.38a2 2 0 0 0-2.73-.73l-.15.08a2 2 0 0 1-2 0l-.43-.25a2 2 0 0 1-1-1.73V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z'></path><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='3'></circle></svg>Supervised Extraction in Beni Mellal</h2><details class='group mb-6 text-gray-600'><summary class='cursor-pointer list-none outline-none leading-relaxed [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden'><span class='group-open:hidden'>Our olives are cold-pressed in the <strong>mills of Beni Mellal</strong>, a region renowned for centuries... <span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] ml-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline'>Read more</span></span><span class='hidden group-open:block'><p class='leading-relaxed mb-3'>Our olives are cold-pressed in the <strong>mills of Beni Mellal</strong>, a region renowned for centuries for the exceptional quality of its olive groves. Each extraction is personally supervised to guarantee acidity below 0.8%.</p><span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline cursor-pointer'>Show less</span></span></summary></details><h2 class='flex items-center mt-10 mb-4'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' class='inline-block mr-3 text-[rgba(212,175,55,0.9)]'><path d='M17.8 19.2 16 11l3.5-3.5C21 6 21.5 4 21 3c-1-.5-3 0-4.5 1.5L13 8 4.8 6.2c-.5-.1-.9.2-1.1.6L3 8l6 4-3 3-3.2-.8c-.4-.1-.8.1-1 .4L1 16l4.2 2.1L8 23l1.4-.8c.3-.2.5-.6.4-1l-.8-3.2 3-3 4 6l1.2-.7c.4-.2.7-.6.6-1.1z'></path></svg>Travel-Ready Packaging</h2><details class='group mb-6 text-gray-600'><summary class='cursor-pointer list-none outline-none leading-relaxed [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden'><span class='group-open:hidden'>Zabra olive oil is stored in food-grade steel canisters designed for travel... <span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] ml-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline'>Read more</span></span><span class='hidden group-open:block'><p class='leading-relaxed mb-3'>Zabra olive oil is stored in food-grade steel canisters designed for travel. Durable and secure, they protect the oil from light and heat, and can be placed directly in luggage without additional wrapping — making them ideal for long journeys.</p><span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline cursor-pointer'>Show less</span></span></summary></details> <p class='leading-relaxed mb-3 italic'>Crafted in Morocco, designed to travel the world.</p>"
        },
        "recipe": {
            "title": "Olive Oil Recipes",
            "content": "<h2 class='flex items-center mt-10 mb-4'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' class='inline-block mr-3 text-[rgba(212,175,55,0.9)]'><path d='M12 12c-2-2.67-4-4-4-6a4 4 0 0 1 8 0c0 2-2 3.33-4 6Z'></path><path d='M12 21a8 8 0 0 0 8-8c0-4.42-4-7-4-7s-.5.5-2 2c-1.5-2-4-5-4-5S6 8.58 6 13a8 8 0 0 0 8 8Z'></path></svg>Moroccan Roasted Pepper Marinade</h2><details class='group mb-6 text-gray-600'><summary class='cursor-pointer list-none outline-none leading-relaxed [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden'><span class='group-open:hidden'>Roast green, red, or yellow peppers until the skin is charred, then marinate with ZABRA olive oil. <span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] ml-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline'>Read more</span></span><span class='hidden group-open:block'><p class='leading-relaxed mb-3'>A classic Moroccan starter bursting with smoky flavor.</p><ul class='list-inside mb-4'><li>Roast green, red, or yellow peppers until the skin is charred.</li><li>Peel off the burnt skin and slice the peppers into thin strips.</li><li>Place in a bowl and generously cover with <strong>ZABRA extra virgin olive oil</strong>.</li><li>Add crushed garlic, chopped parsley, sea salt, and black pepper.</li><li>Let marinate before serving.</li></ul><span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline cursor-pointer'>Show less</span></span></summary></details><h2 class='flex items-center mt-10 mb-4'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' class='inline-block mr-3 text-[rgba(212,175,55,0.9)]'><path d='M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z'></path></svg>Daily Wellness Ritual</h2><details class='group mb-6 text-gray-600'><summary class='cursor-pointer list-none outline-none leading-relaxed [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden'><span class='group-open:hidden'>One tablespoon of extra virgin olive oil every morning on an empty stomach offers remarkable benefits... <span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] ml-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline'>Read more</span></span><span class='hidden group-open:block'><p class='leading-relaxed mb-3'>One tablespoon of extra virgin olive oil every morning on an empty stomach offers remarkable benefits:</p><ul class='list-inside mb-4'><li>Supports <strong>digestion</strong> and protects the gastric lining</li><li>Promotes <strong>heart health</strong> through omega-9 fatty acids</li><li>Hydrates skin from within for a radiant complexion</li></ul><span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline cursor-pointer'>Show less</span></span></summary></details><h2 class='flex items-center mt-10 mb-4'><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' class='inline-block mr-3 text-[rgba(212,175,55,0.9)]'><polygon points='12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2'></polygon></svg>ZABRA Signature Dressing</h2><details class='group mb-6 text-gray-600'><summary class='cursor-pointer list-none outline-none leading-relaxed [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden'><span class='group-open:hidden'>Combine ZABRA extra virgin olive oil, balsamic vinegar, and a hint of Dijon mustard... <span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] ml-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline'>Read more</span></span><span class='hidden group-open:block'><p class='leading-relaxed mb-3'>A simple, elegant dressing for any salad or appetizer.</p><ul class='list-inside mb-4'><li><strong>ZABRA extra virgin olive oil</strong></li><li>Balsamic vinegar</li><li>A hint of Dijon mustard</li><li>A drop of honey</li></ul><span class='text-[rgba(212,175,55,1)] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline cursor-pointer'>Show less</span></span></summary></details><p class='leading-relaxed mb-3 italic'>Season with sea salt and black pepper.</p>"
        }
